last ride is a 2009 australian drama film directed by glendyn ivin .   it is based on the novel the last ride by denise young .   the film follows a young boy ( tom russell ) accompanying his father ( hugo weaving ) , who is wanted by the police , across australia .   the film was given a limited release across australia on 2 july 2009 , and in the united states on 29 june 2012 .